Keldling Bryg
This is a porter made from 8 malts, hops, wolf berries and honey.
It contains approx. 5% alchohol, has a dark color (EBC 63) and is
not really bitter (IBU 21) except its lasting liquorice taste.
This was re-bottled with honey the 26th of March 2016.
WARNING! IT WILL FUR YOU OVER WHEN OPENED!
"Handsome armor. Not a scratch on it." - "You served him well when serving was safe."
- "A madman sees what he sees. " - "I will have no part in it. " - "War was easier
than daughters..." - "The man who passes the sentence should swing the sword."
- "Winter is coming." - Ned Stark in "Game of Thrones" by George R. R. Martin.
